NEXT-HOP-ADDRESS-FAMILY - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-ipv4-bgp-oper:bgp/instances/instance/{instance-name}/instance-active/default-vrf/afs/af/{af-name}/next-hop-address-families/next-hop-address-family/{next-hop-af-name}/

Retrieve operation of resource: next-hop-address-family

instance-name: string
in path

ID of instance-name

af-name: string
in path

ID of af-name

next-hop-af-name: string
in path

ID of next-hop-af-name

200 OK
next-hop-address-family_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error
